ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Attend as many as possible. It sets expectations for your work and your ability to present and it helps you understand what your peers are working on. It may spark a research question.
mandatory and very important for students

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I gained a broader understanding of my field based on the various fields my peers have chosen. I have not yet chosen a dissertation topic, so that part of the question is not applicable.
this will be very important practice in the future
